# Privacy Policy – Todone

**Last updated:** December 2025

## Introduction

Todone is a simple and focused productivity application (Todo & Pomodoro) designed to help users manage their tasks and focus better, without collecting or tracking any personal data.

Your privacy is extremely important to us. This Privacy Policy explains clearly and transparently how Todone handles user data.

## Information Collection and Use

**Todone does NOT collect any personal information.**

Specifically:

* We do **not** collect names, emails, phone numbers, or any identifiers.
* We do **not** collect usage analytics or behavioral data.
* We do **not** track users in any way.
* We do **not** require account creation or login.

All tasks, settings, and app data remain **locally on the user’s device only**.

## Permissions

Todone:

* Does **not** request any device permissions.
* Does **not** access camera, microphone, storage, contacts, location, or any system resources.

If sounds or timers are used inside the app, they operate entirely within the app without accessing or sharing any external data.

## Data Storage

* All data (tasks, timers, preferences) are stored **locally on the device**.
* No data is uploaded to any server.
* No cloud storage or external databases are used.

If the user deletes the app, all stored data is permanently removed.

## Third-Party Services

Todone does **not** use:

* Third-party analytics services
* Advertising networks
* Tracking SDKs
* External APIs that collect user data

## Children’s Privacy

Todone does not knowingly collect any data from anyone, including children under the age of 13. Since no data is collected at all, the app is safe for all age groups.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

If this Privacy Policy is updated in the future, changes will be reflected on this page with an updated revision date.

Any changes will always respect the core principle of Todone: **no data collection, ever**.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, you may contact the developer through the app store listing.

---

**Todone** was built with privacy-first principles.
Your data stays yours. Always.
